---
title: Spiced Paneer & Roasted Veggie Salad with Mint Yoghurt
description: If you haven’t cooked with delicious Indian paneer cheese before, get ready for creaminess that pairs beautifully with big, bold flavours. Toss it all together with a colourful array of roasted veggies, finish with a drizzle of mint yoghurt and voila, you've got yourself a dinner for the senses.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e857333fd1ddb2df045dda3-20f93793.jpg
